ist evidence for the home presentation group","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Inspect target Harmony home/navigation/state implementation for matching endpoints and identify gaps limited to this group","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Implement minimal target repair or verification hooks for this group only","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Update source coverage authority rows for the six home presentation features with precise evidence","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run bounded verification commands and summarize remaining in-scope gaps","status":"pending","priority":"medium"}],"truncated":false},"title":"5 todos","time":{"start":1782402625639,"end":1782402625641}},"id":"prt_eff79af40001BXBpSxcCxymi63","sessionID":"ses_1008692e3ffes7wyEd1LjsXTmN","messageID":"msg_eff799a02001fnyOHZKcntkpLH"}}
