eature verification; cite tests, manual/emulator evidence, or explicit verificationEvidence for behavior closure.\n265: - Use implemented-simplified only with concrete simplification reason, preserved-behavior explanation, target endpoints or tests, and source/platform evidence.\n266: - If a suitable HarmonyOS/Cangjie API, Kit, example, or package exists for a platform capability, use it or record a platform replacement; do not close the item with local mock data, sample data, in-memory simulation, or another fallback.\n267: - Use deferred only for concrete blockers; otherwise implement faithfully or platform-replace with evidence.\n268: - Update source-coverage-matrix.json/md and platform-capability-check.json/md before phase completion.\n269: - If this checklist is empty but the phase has real scope in plan.md/plan.json, assign plannedPhase values first.\n\n(End of file - total 269 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Phase Task Checklist\n\n- Phase: `phase-04-home-history-discovery`\n\n## Purpose\n\nCurrent-phase task checklist generated from the agent-maintained source coverage matrix and platform capability check. Use it before editing and update the matrix/check after work.\n\n## Summary\n\n| metric | value |\n| --- | --- |\n| phaseFeatureEntries | 30 |\n| phaseCriticalHighFeatureEntries | 26 |\n| mustCompleteFeatureEntries | 26 |\n| needsEvidenceFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| deferredOrFallbackFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| coveredFeatureEntries | 0 |\n| phaseSourceFiles | 9 |\n| phasePlatformCapabilityEntries | 0 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\phase-task-checklist.md","time":{"start":1782402632621,"end":1782402632626}},"id":"prt_eff79cb90001PI5fq0ySGoeWrj","sessionID":"ses_1008692e3ffes7wyEd1LjsXTmN","messageID":"msg_eff79b3110019zuJ6jfCwTLcQC"}}
